**STORY**

Once,The Lion King Fell Ill.
Soon, A Foul Smell Started To Come Out To His Body When The Animals Came To Know That Their King Was Ill 
They Went To Meet Him But Even A Few Steps Away Den They Could Smell The Foul Smell
 So They Put Hankies To Their Noses
to keep of the smell.

while meeting the animals the lion asked the reason for that.
bear and zebra spoke up "because bad smell is coming out of your body"
the lion lost his temper at such insulting words and killed them.
the other animals run away to save their lives.
one day the clever fox came to meet the lion and asked the same question the fox replied "your majesty my nose is closed due to cold"
with these words fox saved his lives he knew one must speak according to the situation.